WARNING:HOTPLUG_SECTION: Using __devinit is unnecessary
#153: FILE: drivers/net/irda/bfin_sir.c:34:
+static void __devinit bfin_sir_init_ports(struct bfin_sir_port *sp, struct platform_device *pdev)

CHECK:UNNECESSARY_PARENTHESES: Unnecessary parentheses around sp->rx_dma_timer
#179: FILE: drivers/net/irda/bfin_sir.c:60:
+	init_timer(&(sp->rx_dma_timer));

Parentheses are not required in the following cases:

  1. Function pointer uses::

      (foo->bar)();

    could be::

      foo->bar();

  2. Comparisons in if::

      if ((foo->bar) && (foo->baz))
      if ((foo == bar))

    could be::

      if (foo->bar && foo->baz)
      if (foo == bar)

  3. addressof/dereference single Lvalues::

      &(foo->bar)
      *(foo->bar)

    could be::

      &foo->bar
      *foo->bar

